OL,3,CCornish school faces funding cuts as
OL,4,Csecond homes see pupil numbers dwindle
OL,6,FA small primary school in Cornwall
OL,7,Fsays it is facing funding cuts as an
OL,8,Fincreasing number of second home
OL,9,Fowners buy properties in its village.
OL,10,FPendeen School in West Penwith
OL,11,Fcurrently only has 79 pupils with
OL,12,Fcapacity for 119.
