OL,3,CCornish school faces funding cuts as
OL,4,Csecond homes see pupil numbers dwindle
OL,6,FDr Blunden said the issue of second
OL,7,Fhomes and holiday lets goes beyond
OL,8,Feven the academy trust.
OL,10,FShe added: "This may be the downside
OL,11,Fof living in a beautiful part of
OL,12,FCornwall, but the impact second homes
OL,13,Fand holiday lets have on the local
OL,14,Fhousing market is certainly being felt.
OL,16,F"Local families are being squeezed
OL,17,Fout. While we make some budget changes
OL,18,Fto accommodate this shift, this cannot
OL,19,Fcontinue forever.
