OL,3,CCornish school faces funding cuts as
OL,4,Csecond homes see pupil numbers dwindle
OL,6,F"The school is an essential part of
OL,7,Fvillage life and of the community but
OL,8,Fthe lives of those who live there all
OL,9,Fyear round are certainly being
OL,10,Fimpacted by the housing crisis.
OL,12,F"We need to make sure that young
OL,13,Ffamilies are still able to live here."
OL,14,FShe said the trust is working with the
OL,15,Flocal parish council and Cornwall
OL,16,FCouncil on ways to promote the local
OL,17,Fnursery school, Pendeen School and
OL,18,Feverything the village has to offer to
OL,19,Fyoung families.
